high_descs: Turn around to go to the counter.
Pick the purple cloth from the back of the counter.
Take the cloth and move a few steps to the right.
Place the cloth in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the cloth.
Take the cloth and turn around, then to the right to find the bath tub.
Place the cloth in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a cloth and place it in the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter in front of you then take a step left.
Pick up the purple cloth above the soap dispenser.
Take a step to your right.
Get the cloth wet in the sink then get it back out and close the tap.
Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the tub and turn right.
Put the purple cloth in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet cloth in the tub.

high_descs: Turn to your right then face the sink counter
Pick up the dirty rag on the left side of the sink counter
Turn to your right and move closely to the sink
Put the dirty rag on the sink and rinse it
Pick up the clean rag then turn around to your right head to the tub
Put the clean rag in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put clean rag in the tub
